{
 "name": "RPlog_Saving_Grace",
 "title": "Saving Grace",
 "summary": "Confined for five days to a single room in the Hutt Ullo's stronghold on Tatooine, the captive Lady Ylsa is tended only by her servant Ilyana, who slips a familiar, forbidden song into the music player to wake her hungover mistress. Under the watching eye of a hidden camera, Ilyana cautiously reveals a secret while bathing Ylsa: she has been secretly aiding a man named Paul -- Ylsa's Corellian lover -- who escaped capture aboard the ship and sought the girl out on the streets of Mos Eisley. Passing Ylsa a seashell as proof and relaying Paul's message that he loves her and is devising an escape, Ilyana watches her guarded mistress dissolve into hopeful tears. Ylsa urges caution for Paul's safety, and in a quiet act of intimacy beneath the surveillance, she sets servant and master distinctions aside, inviting the astonished Ilyana to sit and share her meal.",
